### Ping test to a destination 

POST {{server}}/serviceTest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "EXFO Service Assurance Contineous Test (every 1 sec)",   
  "Name":"Ping Active Test",
  "mode" : "PROACTIVE",
  "startDateTime": "2018-05-10 10:00",
  "endDateTime": "2018-05-10 10:05",
  "serviceTestCharacteristic": {
    "name":"com.brixnet.pingactivetest"
  }
}
